        tags: ["Clinical Research", "DNA Damage", "Genetic Mutations", "Genetic Polymorphisms", "Genetic Variants", "Hereditary Cancer", "MC1R", "MC1R Research", "Melanocortin Receptor", "Prevention", "Receptor Biology", "Treatment"]
