        url: "https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21907230/",
        affiliations: "Cancer and Population Studies Group, Queensland Institute of Medical Research, Brisbane, Queensland, Australia. Adele.Green@qimr.edu.au",
        category: "MC1R General",
        teaser: "Red hair genetics and MC1R's role in skin cancer risk",
        tags: ["Cancer Risk", "DNA Damage", "Epidemiology", "Freckles", "MC1R Research", "Melanin", "Melanoma", "Red Hair", "Redhead Phenotype", "Review", "Skin Cancer", "Skin Pigmentation", "Sun Exposure", "UV Radiation"]
