        teaser: "Sunscreen ingredients and their environmental health effects",
        tags: ["Avobenzone", "BP-3", "Benzophenone-3", "Human Exposure", "Human Studies", "In Vitro Study", "Octinoxate", "Octocrylene", "Oxybenzone", "Research Study", "Safety Assessment", "Sunscreen Research", "Toxicity"]
